text: Dermot Dunne (born 5 September 1943) is an Irish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Ireland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
